cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is about extreme multi-label text classification, which is a problem in natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a deep learning-based method, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with large-scale datasets and uses attention mechanisms, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
